sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant SS as /sprint-start
    participant SD as /standup
    participant Cal as ~/.claude/sprints/calendar.md
    participant Cfg as Company Config
    participant FS as docs/sprints/

    H->>SS: /sprint-start

    SS->>Cal: Identify current sprint by today's date
    alt No sprint in calendar
        SS->>H: Generate dates or sync from calendar?
        H->>SS: Choice + dates
    end

    SS->>Cfg: Read sprint_length_weeks, freeze periods, team locales
    SS->>FS: Pull carry-in from previous sprint-NN.md

    SS->>H: Surface top 5 global backlog items — include in sprint?
    H->>SS: Decisions
    SS->>H: Surface active High/Critical known issues — schedule as tickets?
    H->>SS: Decisions

    alt Sprint overlaps freeze period
        SS->>H: ❄️ Freeze [dates] — plan accordingly
    end
    alt Public holidays in sprint window
        SS->>H: ⚠️ [locale] holiday near [date] — verify availability
    end

    SS->>H: Gather sprint goals (1–5) + deadlines + constraints
    H->>SS: Goals confirmed
    SS->>H: Present full draft
    H->>SS: Confirm

    note over SS: Capacity check
    SS->>H: Story points vs limit + token budget vs cap
    alt Over capacity
        SS->>H: ⚠️ Over capacity — defer or accept overload?
        H->>SS: Decision
    end
    alt XL tickets present
        SS->>H: ⚠️ #N is XL — run /break-down before /build
    end

    note over SS: Tech debt check
    SS->>H: High priority tech debt items — schedule any this sprint?
    H->>SS: Decisions

    SS->>FS: Write docs/sprints/sprint-NN.md
    SS->>FS: Update PRD sprint fields + docs/kanban.md

    loop Every session during sprint
        H->>SD: /standup
        SD->>H: Daily brief — token spend + deadline flags + ❄️ freeze warnings
    end
